phrases: Mizuhara Chizuru is just a rental girlfriend.
A fake one who will not last,
and one you are not allowed to really fall for.
When hwill hhyou hhhget hhhhhere hhhhh?
When hwill hhyou hhhget hhhhhere hhhhh?
If you do not hurry up
I will charge you for an extension
Who does that girl think she is?
And that stupid virgin's pissing hme off, too!
Not like they will last more than three months, anyway

Receipt Kinoshita Kazuya-sama Rent-A-Girlfriend Itemized Bill Base Fee/hrhhhhhh 5000 yen x1 hChoice Fee (Rookie)hhhhhhhhh5000 yen x1 hhCosts (City Limits)hhhhhhhhhhhh2000 yen x1 Total: 12,000 yen + taxes
He jumped in to save me?
Not only can I not take care of myself, I even put my client in danger!
I told you, how you deal with me is up to you!
Why put yourself at risk like this when I am not even your real girlfriend?
I keep telling you, I am just a rental girlfriend!
He is not a bad guy, honestly.
How could I ever be angry with the lady who did fall for you?
Two people, seemingly a college couple, fell off the ferry!
The male was wearing an orange T-shirt!
I thought I could do it.
I guess real life is not as easy as movies or manga.
I never got to introduce you to a nice girl.
I could not even clean up my own mess.
I am sorry you had to jump in to save me.
the Coast Guard guys gave us a royal chewing-out.
Then our friends snapped at us.
Ultimately, I skipped out on meeting Mami-chan
and had to spend the night in a nearby hospital.
For, you know... doing all that to save me.
She just said girlfriend, present tense.
Mizuhara's a rental girlfriend, and real mature.
She would not think anything of a mere kiss.
Hey, there is the big hero.
Are not you guys even a little worried about me?
Oh, she said she was going back home.
Thanks for coming to pick me up.
Of course she hates me now.
It is back to the drawing board!
Quit standing around and get in, Kazuya!
Do not drown in the bathtub.
Come save me if I do.
I will not tell Nagomi-san about the stupid blues thing.
No, we are still breaking up.
You are still going on about that?
This is way more complicated than you think.
Why did you hit me again, jerk?!
Life are not as easy as you think,
but it are not as hard as people make it out to be.
You put your life on the line for her.
If that is not love, then what the hell is?
Your entire lifetime supply of semen depends on it.
Do not forget her cold stare when she demands you fork over the money!
Her face might be smiling, but her eyes are not!
Could you go be gross somewhere else?
I-I already made the booking for next week.
I will put the money in your post box.
That was just CPR to keep her client alive.
Only a fool would fall for a girl like that for real.
Cannot you even lay low for two days in a row?
This is going to be a big one.
You are such a bad boy, Kazu-kun.
Whenever you find yourself feeling like a rabbit,
You can rent me out for just one hour every Wednesday.
You know you cannot do that.
If you want, I can give you both.
I am Mizuhara Chizuru, Kazuya-san's girlfriend.
I guess you can be a man if you try.
If I told her this was how it all began, Mizuhara would be pissed.
But that was definitely the moment I realized...
What did you do over summer break?
You do know that urban legend about summer break, right?
My tummy started hurting really badly...
Oh, we met at the beach.
I have never reacted to her like that...
Hey, keep your eyes on the road.
Why are we going into the mountains?
I snagged a booking for a hot springs resort known for helping your organs recover.
I hear they serve pheasant for dinner.
It is Mt. Akagi's local specialty!
Have not had any since I got some from a customer at the bar...
Well, cannot complain if it is for health.
Nashigi-kan, Gunma's hidden-away hot springs resort!
And we can get up to thirty ice creams from the lobby machine at no extra charge!
I would spend all day on the can!
Is our friend not here yet?
Thank you for looking after my mother in the hospital.
No, I should be the one thanking her.
She got all better and was discharged, too,
so we decided to go on a trip together to celebrate.
Thank you so much for inviting me.
I am just wondering if the person whose name starts with Chi is here, too.
None of our hospital buddies had a name like that.
I could only get one room in the luxury Haseo-tei,
so I got you one elsewhere.
Do you want to force Ichinose-san into a regular room?
Wow, I have such an understanding grandson.
Did the previous guest leave those?
Well, I guess I can chill out more by myself.
I feel bad'because our grandmas seem to be having fun,
but I have to tell them during this trip that we broke up.
Can you help me do my hair?
The Grandma Axis is conspiring to get the grandkids to form an alliance!
I do not mind them getting along,
but they are meddling too much in our affairs.
I am giving them a piece of my mind!
Oh, right, closed elevator and all.
I was waiting for you in the room!
Look, we had them arrange for yukata and personalized dinners for us.
Changing rooms now would inconvenience the hotel staff.
Sure, but sharing a room is too much.
We have not crossed that line yet.
You have not done it yet?
Well, no time like the present.
Run along to your room now, you two.
Telling them we broke up now would just ruin the trip.
We could ask for another room, I guess...
I am low this month, too.
Sharing a hotel room with a client is a disaster.
Yukata Mizuhara is out of this world!
There is no way I would last an entire night with her in the same room.
I am just going to enjoy this.
My grandmom paid a small fortune for this.
Cannot let it go to waste!
I know it is awkward, but this cannot keep going on.
I am going to tell them we broke up.
Am I living the lucky lecher trope now?!
It was all a lie I told.
My feelings do not factor into it.
So that trope only counts when it is the opposite sex?
You learn something new every day.
Um, Mrs. Kinoshita, I should not be making you do this.
It Is an honor to be washing my future granddaughter-in-law's sultry back.
What is sexy about a back?
Says the girl with this spunky bottom
You are truly a ray of hope that shines upon us Kinoshitas.
I will take great care to wash you inside and out.
After all, the father's genes will not be worth squat.
Uh, you do not have to.
This is also a remembrance trip, you see.
Today's the date my husband passed.
Oh, do not worry about me.
That said, it was always a day that made me feel a little lonely,
but I got out of the hospital, made a new friend,
and even got to take a bath with you.
It has become a special day for me now.
What would you do if I were lying?
What if I were not the kind of person you think I am?
Nobody goes through life without lying.
I would love you even if you were an alien.
I have given up on trying to figure out this mess!
Got To get our money's worth!
Uh, is not that the sauce?
I have never seen her laugh like a normal girl before.
I guess I really am a bother to her.
I can sleep in the bathroom or by the door.
I know you will not have pleasant dreams with me around.
Why cannot you just sleep here?
Already a chief at her young age
I need your help with homework!
Mrs. Kinoshita, there is something we must tell you.
You are finally doing the deed, right?
This is the best day of my life!
